    </statement>
    <statement id="189.txt-17">
      <text>Cypselae oblong, compressed, (apices denticulate), faces ribbed, wrinkled, with long, ascending hairs, basal attachment scars lateral, surrounded by whitish, swollen rims;</text>
      <structure id="o2539" name="cypsela">
